              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": ".  It's not about geometry, not really; but it does two related things:\n(1) Categorizing objects based on their properties e.g. a quadrilateral is a figure with four strait sides, in a trapezoid one pair of sides is parallel, in a parallelogram both pairs of sides are  parallel.\n(2) Constraint propagation e.g. line a is parallel to line b, line b is parallel to line c, so line a is parallel to line c."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
